This module adds a sale_subscription_template model (from
`subscription_oca` module) to products. The aim is to have expiration
dates for products that are not services, but products that have a
subscription model (e.g. magazines, newspapers, etc.). Sets the end date
of contract lines associated to products with a sale subscription
template.

**Table of contents**

.. contents::
   :local:

***************
 Configuration
***************

No configuration required

*******
 Usage
*******

Create sale subscription templates and link them to products by the main
form view of the product. When a contract is created with a product that
has a sale subscription template, the contract lines will be created
with the end date set to the end date of the sale subscription template.

